# Next steps {% #next-steps %}

With SMTP and templates driven from code, every customer's project sends mail that carries their brand rather than yours. From here:

- [Provision a project's baseline](/docs/platforms/project/provisioning) so branding the emails is one step in onboarding.
- Read the [SMTP](/docs/platforms/project/smtp) and [Email templates](/docs/platforms/project/email-templates) references for every field you can set.
